Post-Graduation Outcomes






Post-Graduation Outcomes






            outcomes
          Heading link



 
Copy link



Where can your graduate education lead you? Our alumni demonstrate that a computer science degree from UIC can represent a prelude to highly compensated industry jobs, sought-after postdoctoral research positions, and tenure-track appointments at universities around the world.
UIC computer science graduate students recently have moved on to:






